00:03:50,521 --> 00:03:53,817
to slice and dice, and sift it out.

62
00:03:54,109 --> 00:03:56,319
And now for the winner...

63
00:03:56,402 --> 00:03:58,070
[audience cheering]

64
00:03:58,947 --> 00:04:00,198
Sharl...

65
00:04:02,742 --> 00:04:03,743
Oh, man.

66
00:04:04,578 --> 00:04:05,954
You are...

67
00:04:07,997 --> 00:04:10,332
- not the winner!
- Oh, come on!

68
00:04:10,542 --> 00:04:11,585
[mouthing] I'm sorry.

69
00:04:11,877 --> 00:04:13,461
I'm out of here. This is [bleep].

70
00:04:13,544 --> 00:04:14,628
These two wouldn't know the difference

71
00:04:14,712 --> 00:04:16,298
