205
00:12:21,908 --> 00:12:25,077
He's a huge talent. Shane Roarke.

206
00:12:26,203 --> 00:12:27,205
Come out, buddy!

207
00:12:28,331 --> 00:12:29,456
Oh!

208
00:12:33,336 --> 00:12:36,463
It's Shane Roarke! He's not a guest!

209
00:12:36,588 --> 00:12:39,509
- He's with us!
- Uh-huh. Yup. [chuckles]

210
00:12:39,967 --> 00:12:42,552
Now, I know Shane wanted to get started
meeting all of his staff.

211
00:12:42,636 --> 00:12:45,181
And we all have a lot of work to do
getting ready for Christmas.

212
00:12:45,306 --> 00:12:48,934
So, let's welcome Shane,
and make him feel at home.

213
00:12:50,144 --> 00:12:51,062
Thank you.

214
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:58,110
