218
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:05,451
[laughs] But who cares?

219
00:13:05,534 --> 00:13:09,080
I'm Bonnie. And you're Shane.

220
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:10,498
Hi, Bonnie.

221
00:13:11,081 --> 00:13:13,208
[giggling] Yeah,
Clara was holding my purse.

222
00:13:13,583 --> 00:13:15,586
Oh! Well, that's very nice of her.

223
00:13:16,421 --> 00:13:17,296
- [chuckles]
- [Bonnie] She thinks

224
00:13:17,379 --> 00:13:19,465
I'm lactose intolerant,
but I don't think I am.

225
00:13:19,548 --> 00:13:22,467
Bonnie, remember we talked
about first impressions?

226
00:13:23,052 --> 00:13:25,138
[Shane] OK. Uh, I mean,
that's great to know,

227
00:13:25,221 --> 00:13:27,597
if I'm ever preparing something
for you in the kitchen.

228
00:13:28,224 --> 00:13:30,851
- [all three laugh]
- Yeah.

229
00:13:32,227 --> 00:13:33,479
It was nice to meet you.

230
00:13:34,563 --> 00:13:36,149
Uh-huh. Huh.

231
00:13:37,984 --> 00:13:39,943
- [Clara laughs]
- Wow! No,

232
00:13:40,028 --> 00:13:42,113
that guy needs to take it down a notch
with the flirting.

233
00:13:42,196 --> 00:13:44,032
