957
00:57:51,635 --> 00:57:53,010
- What?
- I want to tell you something.

958
00:57:53,887 --> 00:57:54,721
OK.

959
00:57:56,264 --> 00:57:58,474
I'm not supposed to say
anything, but, um...

960
00:57:59,601 --> 00:58:01,311
